>>So I want to
talk about the God

00:00:13.130 --> 00:00:15.170 align:middle line:84%
Particle for a moment
in relationship

00:00:15.170 --> 00:00:19.780 align:middle line:84%
to this cosmic sap and all
that we've been discussing.

00:00:19.780 --> 00:00:22.260 align:middle line:84%
Y'all have probably heard
that in Geneva, Switzerland,

00:00:22.260 --> 00:00:25.070 align:middle line:84%
we have a little machine called
a particle accelerator there.

00:00:25.070 --> 00:00:30.430 align:middle line:84%
It's a 17-mile around ring, an
accelerator where scientists

00:00:30.430 --> 00:00:34.380 align:middle line:84%
are hoping to start smashing
protons together and learn

00:00:34.380 --> 00:00:35.550 align:middle line:90%
the secrets of the universe.

00:00:35.550 --> 00:00:41.150 align:middle line:84%
They also believe they'll be
able to create baby black holes

00:00:41.150 --> 00:00:43.400 align:middle line:84%
and recreate the conditions
that existed just

00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:46.360 align:middle line:90%
after the Big Bang.

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:49.300 align:middle line:84%
When we talk about rings
of cosmic sovereignty,

00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:51.650 align:middle line:84%
that's where I think we're
building there in Geneva.

00:00:51.650 --> 00:00:54.230 align:middle line:84%
And we're a long way
from these guys here.

00:00:54.230 --> 00:00:56.590 align:middle line:84%
I mean, ours are
17 miles around.

00:00:56.590 --> 00:00:59.070 align:middle line:84%
These guys had one that fit
in the palm of your hand.

00:00:59.070 --> 00:01:01.790 align:middle line:84%
So we've got a long way to
go towards miniaturizing

00:01:01.790 --> 00:01:03.030 align:middle line:90%
these particle accelerators.

00:01:03.030 --> 00:01:04.571 align:middle line:84%
But I think that's
what we're talking

00:01:04.571 --> 00:01:08.210 align:middle line:84%
about when we're talking about
the ring of cosmic sovereignty.

00:01:08.210 --> 00:01:10.120 align:middle line:84%
And I mentioned
earlier that Jesus

00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:12.235 align:middle line:84%
had one of these rings
of cosmic sovereignty.

00:01:12.235 --> 00:01:14.960 align:middle line:90%
He also had a magic wand.

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:16.890 align:middle line:84%
There are two types of
particle accelerators

00:01:16.890 --> 00:01:19.380 align:middle line:84%
that we build today, the
linear accelerators like you

00:01:19.380 --> 00:01:22.100 align:middle line:84%
have in Batavia,
Illinois at Fermilab,

00:01:22.100 --> 00:01:23.910 align:middle line:84%
I visited there
as well, and then

00:01:23.910 --> 00:01:25.810 align:middle line:84%
you have the ring-type
accelerator as you

00:01:25.810 --> 00:01:27.310 align:middle line:90%
have at Geneva.

00:01:27.310 --> 00:01:29.445 align:middle line:84%
So we have the rod and
the ring in Jesus' hand,

00:01:29.445 --> 00:01:32.450 align:middle line:84%
and I wonder if he's in fact
using some kind of a particle

00:01:32.450 --> 00:01:34.530 align:middle line:90%
accelerator here.

00:01:34.530 --> 00:01:37.835 align:middle line:84%
This is the ring at
CERN, 17 miles around.

00:01:37.835 --> 00:01:39.125 align:middle line:90%
It encompasses part of Geneva.

00:01:39.125 --> 00:01:40.940 align:middle line:90%
It goes on into France as well.

00:01:40.940 --> 00:01:43.970 align:middle line:90%
It's all underground.

00:01:43.970 --> 00:01:47.196 align:middle line:84%
I toured their last
summer, the summer of 2007.

00:01:47.196 --> 00:01:48.570 align:middle line:84%
And I went there
because I wanted

00:01:48.570 --> 00:01:51.330 align:middle line:84%
to explore the signs and
symbols of the place.

00:01:51.330 --> 00:01:52.800 align:middle line:84%
Very interested in
this high energy

00:01:52.800 --> 00:01:54.000 align:middle line:90%
physics work that they're doing.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.583 align:middle line:84%
But I wanted to see, what kind
of artwork did they have there?

00:01:56.583 --> 00:01:59.620 align:middle line:84%
What kind of symbolism
did they choose here?

00:01:59.620 --> 00:02:03.790 align:middle line:84%
And what does that tell us
about what is going on there?

00:02:03.790 --> 00:02:05.584 align:middle line:84%
One of the key pieces
of religious art,

00:02:05.584 --> 00:02:07.500 align:middle line:84%
perhaps the only piece
of religious art there,

00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:11.840 align:middle line:84%
is this beautiful statue of
Shiva stamping out ignorance.

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:14.640 align:middle line:84%
Shiva, of course, is the
Lord of the Ring shown

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:16.960 align:middle line:84%
within the ring of
cosmic sovereignty,

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:19.370 align:middle line:84%
and it aligns it with
this idea that what

00:02:19.370 --> 00:02:24.160 align:middle line:84%
we're really trying to do at
CERN is to become ring lords.

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:28.910 align:middle line:84%
If we're successful in detecting
the God particle at CERN,

00:02:28.910 --> 00:02:32.010 align:middle line:84%
it will enable us to graduate
from cosmic kindergarten, where

00:02:32.010 --> 00:02:33.930 align:middle line:84%
we're at right now
metaphorically speaking,

00:02:33.930 --> 00:02:35.350 align:middle line:90%
to first grade.

00:02:35.350 --> 00:02:38.490 align:middle line:84%
We will become full-blown
cosmic citizens.

00:02:38.490 --> 00:02:41.350 align:middle line:84%
So what happens is is you
go 300 feet underground.

00:02:41.350 --> 00:02:42.790 align:middle line:90%
You take the elevator down.

00:02:42.790 --> 00:02:47.740 align:middle line:84%
And this is the hallway leading
into what they called the ATLAS

00:02:47.740 --> 00:02:50.060 align:middle line:84%
Detector, which is the
actual machine that's

00:02:50.060 --> 00:02:53.940 align:middle line:84%
being used to detect what
they call the God Particle.

00:02:53.940 --> 00:02:56.460 align:middle line:84%
The ATLAS Detector is
an enormous machine.

00:02:56.460 --> 00:02:58.710 align:middle line:84%
In fact, they call the
pit that this thing

00:02:58.710 --> 00:03:01.520 align:middle line:90%
sits in a cathedral of science.

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:04.690 align:middle line:84%
So they do use some interesting
religious terminology when

00:03:04.690 --> 00:03:06.430 align:middle line:90%
describing the search here.

00:03:06.430 --> 00:03:10.110 align:middle line:84%
This is a man standing in
front of the ATLAS Detector.

00:03:10.110 --> 00:03:13.130 align:middle line:84%
You can see that it's
just absolutely enormous,

00:03:13.130 --> 00:03:14.630 align:middle line:90%
many stories high.

00:03:14.630 --> 00:03:17.110 align:middle line:84%
One of the most sophisticated
and expensive pieces

00:03:17.110 --> 00:03:21.780 align:middle line:84%
of machinery ever
built by humankind.

00:03:21.780 --> 00:03:24.010 align:middle line:84%
This is me standing
beside the ATLAS Detector.

00:03:24.010 --> 00:03:27.316 align:middle line:84%
You can't even get the whole
thing into a photograph

00:03:27.316 --> 00:03:28.440 align:middle line:90%
when you're standing there.

00:03:28.440 --> 00:03:31.267 align:middle line:84%
And it was a real privilege
be able to go in there.

00:03:31.267 --> 00:03:33.600 align:middle line:84%
Look at the symbolism they
chose for the ATLAS Detector.

00:03:33.600 --> 00:03:35.100 align:middle line:84%
They went back to
the ancient world,

00:03:35.100 --> 00:03:38.580 align:middle line:84%
and they pulled Atlas out of
the hat-- Atlas, who lifted

00:03:38.580 --> 00:03:40.620 align:middle line:90%
the world on his shoulders.

00:03:40.620 --> 00:03:42.830 align:middle line:84%
But it's actually not
the world that Atlas

00:03:42.830 --> 00:03:43.780 align:middle line:90%
has on his shoulders.

00:03:43.780 --> 00:03:46.870 align:middle line:84%
When you look closely,
it's actually a zodiac.

00:03:46.870 --> 00:03:50.440 align:middle line:90%
A zodiac is a gate of stars.

00:03:50.440 --> 00:03:52.720 align:middle line:84%
So maybe what they're
trying to hint at here

00:03:52.720 --> 00:03:55.840 align:middle line:84%
is that Atlas is not only
going to be detecting the God

00:03:55.840 --> 00:03:59.530 align:middle line:84%
Particle and help us to lift
our world, or the Word, the life

00:03:59.530 --> 00:04:01.840 align:middle line:84%
force energy, on our
shoulders, but maybe it

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:05.120 align:middle line:84%
has some kind of stargate
significance as well.

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:07.130 align:middle line:84%
So I've been working
on this kind of angle

00:04:07.130 --> 00:04:09.180 align:middle line:90%
on this for several years.

00:04:09.180 --> 00:04:11.250 align:middle line:84%
And I'm going to
share with you today

00:04:11.250 --> 00:04:14.260 align:middle line:84%
some interesting comments by
one of the scientists working

00:04:14.260 --> 00:04:19.209 align:middle line:84%
at CERN that supports
my contention here.

00:04:19.209 --> 00:04:20.779 align:middle line:84%
The Large Hadron
Collider, as I said,

00:04:20.779 --> 00:04:22.910 align:middle line:84%
is designed to create
baby black holes,

00:04:22.910 --> 00:04:25.750 align:middle line:84%
creating a scenario
that's intended

00:04:25.750 --> 00:04:28.050 align:middle line:84%
to replicate the
conditions present one

00:04:28.050 --> 00:04:30.490 align:middle line:84%
billionth of a second after
the so-called Big Bang

00:04:30.490 --> 00:04:32.830 align:middle line:90%
that formed the universe.

00:04:32.830 --> 00:04:34.710 align:middle line:84%
I talked about this
in my presentation

00:04:34.710 --> 00:04:38.110 align:middle line:84%
Revelation 2012, so I'll
just briefly explain

00:04:38.110 --> 00:04:41.390 align:middle line:84%
why I was so excited when
I came down that elevator,

00:04:41.390 --> 00:04:44.390 align:middle line:84%
the doors open, and were
greeted by this sign.

00:04:44.390 --> 00:04:47.670 align:middle line:84%
"Recreating the conditions
just after the Big Bang,"

00:04:47.670 --> 00:04:51.060 align:middle line:84%
that is the purpose of the
Large Hadron Collider at CERN.

00:04:51.060 --> 00:04:53.280 align:middle line:84%
It's to recreate
these conditions,

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:55.680 align:middle line:84%
and therefore detect
the God Particle,

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:58.020 align:middle line:84%
this elusive subatomic
particle that

00:04:58.020 --> 00:05:00.250 align:middle line:84%
will explain why
all matter has mass,

00:05:00.250 --> 00:05:03.810 align:middle line:84%
and ultimately complete our
physics kit-- taking us out

00:05:03.810 --> 00:05:06.260 align:middle line:84%
of, again, cosmic
kindergarten wondering what's

00:05:06.260 --> 00:05:09.100 align:middle line:84%
up into first grade,
cosmically speaking,

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:13.660 align:middle line:84%
where we have the ring of
cosmic sovereignty in our hand.

00:05:13.660 --> 00:05:15.300 align:middle line:90%
Why was that so important to me?

00:05:15.300 --> 00:05:17.790 align:middle line:84%
Well, for a long time,
I had been researching

00:05:17.790 --> 00:05:20.700 align:middle line:84%
the messianic prophecies and
the Jewish legends of the herald

00:05:20.700 --> 00:05:22.390 align:middle line:90%
or forerunner of the Messiah.

00:05:22.390 --> 00:05:25.920 align:middle line:84%
This figure has a to-do list,
according to Jewish legend--

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:28.910 align:middle line:84%
get the Ark of the
Covenant, get the manna,

00:05:28.910 --> 00:05:30.840 align:middle line:90%
get the anointing oil.

00:05:30.840 --> 00:05:32.880 align:middle line:84%
We've talked about
several of these things.

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:38.120 align:middle line:84%
And also, recreate the
conditions-- well, excuse me.

00:05:38.120 --> 00:05:39.650 align:middle line:90%
Here's the exact quote.

00:05:39.650 --> 00:05:42.470 align:middle line:10%
"The Messiah will have
Elijah blow the trumpet,

00:05:42.470 --> 00:05:45.030 align:middle line:10%
and at the first
sound, the primal light

00:05:45.030 --> 00:05:48.242 align:middle line:10%
which shown before the week
of creation will reappear.

00:05:48.242 --> 00:05:50.075 align:middle line:10%
And at the second sound,
the dead will rise,

00:05:50.075 --> 00:05:52.700 align:middle line:10%
and with this swiftness of wind,
assemble around the Messiah

00:05:52.700 --> 00:05:54.210 align:middle line:10%
from all corners of the Earth.

00:05:54.210 --> 00:05:56.020 align:middle line:84%
And at the third
sound, the Shekhinah

00:05:56.020 --> 00:05:59.490 align:middle line:90%
will become visible to all."

00:05:59.490 --> 00:06:01.970 align:middle line:84%
The primal light which
shown before the first week

00:06:01.970 --> 00:06:05.440 align:middle line:84%
of creation, recreating
the conditions just

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:07.410 align:middle line:90%
after the Big Bang.

00:06:07.410 --> 00:06:09.140 align:middle line:84%
Sounds to me like
they're talking

00:06:09.140 --> 00:06:12.280 align:middle line:84%
about the exact
same moment in time.

00:06:12.280 --> 00:06:14.490 align:middle line:10%
This herald or
forerunner is charged

00:06:14.490 --> 00:06:18.620 align:middle line:10%
with revealing the light which
shown before the first week

00:06:18.620 --> 00:06:19.750 align:middle line:10%
of creation.

00:06:19.750 --> 00:06:22.390 align:middle line:84%
At CERN, they're recreating
the conditions just

00:06:22.390 --> 00:06:25.160 align:middle line:84%
after the Big Bang, a
billionth of a second

00:06:25.160 --> 00:06:27.300 align:middle line:84%
after the Big Bang,
which to me sounds

00:06:27.300 --> 00:06:31.440 align:middle line:84%
like that's just before
the first week of creation.

00:06:31.440 --> 00:06:34.110 align:middle line:84%
I'm thinking we've got
a perfect match here,

00:06:34.110 --> 00:06:37.290 align:middle line:84%
that what our collective
conscious is doing right now

00:06:37.290 --> 00:06:42.990 align:middle line:84%
is checking off another of the
items on the to-do list here.

00:06:42.990 --> 00:06:44.470 align:middle line:84%
And what happens
after that, this

00:06:44.470 --> 00:06:46.520 align:middle line:90%
is when the dead will rise.

00:06:46.520 --> 00:06:49.430 align:middle line:84%
We are the dead,
as I said earlier.

00:06:49.430 --> 00:06:51.850 align:middle line:84%
If we're successful in
detecting the God Particle,

00:06:51.850 --> 00:06:54.544 align:middle line:84%
we will go from cosmic
kindergarten to first grade.

00:06:54.544 --> 00:06:56.210 align:middle line:84%
But another way of
describing that is we

00:06:56.210 --> 00:07:00.710 align:middle line:84%
will go from dead to
alive, cosmically speaking.

00:07:00.710 --> 00:07:04.370 align:middle line:84%
And everything else starts
to open up from there.

00:07:04.370 --> 00:07:06.910 align:middle line:10%
Remember Jesus said, I am the
light that is over all things.

00:07:06.910 --> 00:07:08.210 align:middle line:10%
I am from all.

00:07:08.210 --> 00:07:11.880 align:middle line:10%
From me, all came forth,
and to me, all attained.

00:07:11.880 --> 00:07:12.730 align:middle line:10%
Lift the stone.

00:07:12.730 --> 00:07:13.730 align:middle line:10%
Split the wood.

00:07:13.730 --> 00:07:15.280 align:middle line:10%
There I am.

00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:18.720 align:middle line:84%
And that's what science
is doing at CERN.

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:20.790 align:middle line:84%
They're preparing
to split the wood

00:07:20.790 --> 00:07:23.550 align:middle line:84%
by slamming these
protons together

00:07:23.550 --> 00:07:25.250 align:middle line:84%
in hopes of
discovering or seeing

00:07:25.250 --> 00:07:28.605 align:middle line:84%
this elusive subatomic particle
they call the God Particle.

00:07:28.605 --> 00:07:31.177 align:middle line:90%


00:07:31.177 --> 00:07:32.760 align:middle line:84%
Something that
intrigued me about this

00:07:32.760 --> 00:07:36.830 align:middle line:84%
is compare the symbolism of the
Large Hadron Collider, which

00:07:36.830 --> 00:07:39.820 align:middle line:84%
is an eight-spoked wheel,
with the Maya symbol

00:07:39.820 --> 00:07:44.380 align:middle line:84%
of the galactic center, which
is also an eight-spoked wheel.

00:07:44.380 --> 00:07:44.939 align:middle line:90%
Hm.

00:07:44.939 --> 00:07:47.230 align:middle line:84%
That's kind of fascinating--
a little bit of "as above,

00:07:47.230 --> 00:07:49.420 align:middle line:90%
so below" action going on there.

00:07:49.420 --> 00:07:53.050 align:middle line:84%
This is the way CERN portrays
the collision of these protons.

00:07:53.050 --> 00:07:55.780 align:middle line:84%
Looks like someone had
a bad hangover to me.

00:07:55.780 --> 00:07:58.950 align:middle line:10%
But the ideas is expressed, once
again, that what we're doing

00:07:58.950 --> 00:08:02.920 align:middle line:10%
is colliding these particles,
and that ultimately,

00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:04.900 align:middle line:10%
what is going to
emerge out of this

00:08:04.900 --> 00:08:08.430 align:middle line:10%
is a new science,
a new beginning,

00:08:08.430 --> 00:08:10.764 align:middle line:10%
a new dawn for humankind.

00:08:10.764 --> 00:08:12.180 align:middle line:84%
This God Particle,
as I mentioned,

00:08:12.180 --> 00:08:15.960 align:middle line:84%
is supposed to be the key to
explaining why matter has mass.

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:19.920 align:middle line:84%
And with it, we will become,
effectively, godlike beings.

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:23.990 align:middle line:84%
Here's another simulation of
the detector at the Large Hadron

00:08:23.990 --> 00:08:27.710 align:middle line:84%
Collider of these
protons colliding.

00:08:27.710 --> 00:08:29.410 align:middle line:90%
I found this other image here.

00:08:29.410 --> 00:08:34.299 align:middle line:84%
It's the dove spitting the
symbol for the God Particle.

00:08:34.299 --> 00:08:36.340 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's really
interesting because CERN

00:08:36.340 --> 00:08:38.789 align:middle line:84%
was founded by European
high energy physics types.

00:08:38.789 --> 00:08:42.120 align:middle line:84%
After World War II, they watched
as all the Nazi high energy

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:45.180 align:middle line:84%
physics types went to
Russia or the United States.

00:08:45.180 --> 00:08:46.930 align:middle line:84%
The Europeans grew
concerned, because they

00:08:46.930 --> 00:08:49.650 align:middle line:84%
knew if the Nazi high energy
physics types were involved,

00:08:49.650 --> 00:08:51.260 align:middle line:84%
they're going to
weaponize whatever

00:08:51.260 --> 00:08:53.360 align:middle line:90%
it is that they discover.

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:55.440 align:middle line:84%
They all came over here,
went to work for NASA,

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:56.764 align:middle line:90%
went to work in US labs.

00:08:56.764 --> 00:08:59.180 align:middle line:84%
And for all we know, they may
have already discovered this

00:08:59.180 --> 00:09:03.260 align:middle line:84%
and are, in fact, already
weaponizing this knowledge.

00:09:03.260 --> 00:09:05.860 align:middle line:84%
So the Europeans said, we want
to get together and create

00:09:05.860 --> 00:09:07.790 align:middle line:84%
a particle accelerator
that will be used only

00:09:07.790 --> 00:09:09.430 align:middle line:90%
for peaceful purposes.

00:09:09.430 --> 00:09:12.910 align:middle line:84%
Hence, the symbol of the dove,
which is the symbol for peace.

00:09:12.910 --> 00:09:16.780 align:middle line:84%
But in Christianity, the dove is
the symbol for the Holy Spirit.

00:09:16.780 --> 00:09:19.480 align:middle line:84%
It's the symbol for Christ,
as a matter of fact.

00:09:19.480 --> 00:09:21.840 align:middle line:84%
And so here we have the
symbol of the Holy Spirit

00:09:21.840 --> 00:09:24.029 align:middle line:84%
spitting the God
Particle, or dare

00:09:24.029 --> 00:09:25.820 align:middle line:84%
we just go ahead and
call it what it really

00:09:25.820 --> 00:09:28.840 align:middle line:90%
is, the Christ Particle.

00:09:28.840 --> 00:09:32.600 align:middle line:84%
That's what we're really
talking about here.

00:09:32.600 --> 00:09:36.380 align:middle line:84%
So here's the stylized
logo of the God

00:09:36.380 --> 00:09:38.460 align:middle line:84%
Particle, the collision
of the protons

00:09:38.460 --> 00:09:41.610 align:middle line:84%
that will ultimately
reveal the God Particle.

00:09:41.610 --> 00:09:44.490 align:middle line:84%
This is a particle physics news
and resources newsletter where

00:09:44.490 --> 00:09:46.870 align:middle line:90%
they use this stylized logo.

